{"tid":630500,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[日經]有無人同我一樣返工返得好唔開心","createTime":"2018-04-15T16:06:15.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-16T15:54:16.000Z","uid":154302,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"1eb15f15728f75ceabba5c2865cfb09b06f871ee","tid":630500,"uid":154302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-15T16:06:15.000Z","msg":"但又唔可以走<br />\n事關只係調左職兩個月<br />\n走左份CV就花哂<br />\n二黎又好難搵翻相似嘅位置<br />\n<br />\n但每日諗起第二日要返工就好鬱悶<br />\n啲人事好似就嚟搞到自己要精神病咁<br />\n覺得做人好唔開心 冇得選擇咁<br />\n但我又知道好多人同我一樣 <br />\n就會諗自己係咪太幼稚冇能力先會咁唔開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"17a59e5af8832a48a99cebc67cc49bb7d1dcbd09","tid":630500,"uid":154302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-15T16:21:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 得我尻流流咁<br />\n唉聽日就星期一"},{"pid":"87f3c65d3a8d9632debf6f94873d655779420574","tid":630500,"uid":37565,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-16T15:54:16.000Z","msg":"中學定小學"}]}